svg.desc: Page template for a single page with a background panel that takes up about 40% of the page. The background panel is partially covered, used for atmosphere and should not contain any characters or objects. The 7 foreground panels are the main content of the page and can contain characters and objects. The foreground panels are of equal width and height.

rect.data-info: half-page background panel for atmosphere; do not use characters objects as it is partially covered by further panels
1st panel; top row; first panel from the left
2nd panel; top row; second panel from the left
3rd panel; middle row; first panel from the left
4th panel; middle row; second panel from the left
5th panel; middle row; third panel from the left
6th panel; bottom row; first panel from the left
7th panel; bottom row; second panel from the left
